node.text:
Dales dream is to finally travel again, get out of the city and go to Europe! We looked up flights to France and surprised him with $500 to start his travel fund and a brand new suitcase!!! We had to bring Dales vision to life in every way possible! Europe is waiting for you brother 🚀

You guys DONATE, we can make DREAMS happen... link is in my bio!!

node.text: Timmy has been in the ER fighting for his life everyday this week 😔 He is finding it hard to breath on his own and is struggling a lot. Timmy is the biggest dreamer in the world! Timmy went from being a fan of mine. To writing down one day he would work with me. To then one day meeting me. To one day coming on tour with me as an intern to then becoming the C.O.O. of the dream machine foundation. Please pray for @timmy.the.dreamer guys 🙏 Please send him all the love and prayers ❤️
